At present, our authorized partners include the following types: suppliers, service providers and other partners. We send information to suppliers, service providers and other partners who support our business, including basic technical services, consulting, analysis and other professional services.
We will sign strict confidentiality agreements and other companies, institutions and with whom to share user information, personal information protection agreements, and require them to deal with users in accordance with our instructions, the privacy policy and other related confidentiality and security measures. information.

